Sintaxis

+router ospf [pid] // 1 -> 65535
+network [id red] [mascara comodin] area [id area]
+interface loopback [número]
+bandwidth [kbps]
+ip ospf authentication-key [contraseña]
+ip ospf hello-interval [segundos]
+ip ospf dead-interval [segundos]
+area [id area] authentication
+area [id area] authentication message-digest
+redistribute static
+area [id area] virtual-link [id enrutador]
+redistribute rip subnets
+show ip ospf interface
+show ip ospf database
+show ip ospf neighbor
+show ip route

==========================================================

R8>ena
R8(config)#router ospf 10
R8(config-router)#network 13.0.0.0 0.255.255.255 area 3
#network 15.0.0.0 0.255.255.255 area 4

// Máscara comodín = broadcast - Máscara subred => 255.255.255.255 - 255.0.0.0 = 0.255.255.255

#area 3 virtual-link 11.255.255.254 // Si no queremos calcularlo, usamos +show ip ospf interface, o definiendo una interfaz con +interface loopback [número] y configurándola con 

========================================================

Conf. R5
R5#conf t
R5(config)#router ospf 5
R5(config-router)#network 5.0.0.0 0.255.255.255 area 0
	#network 6.0.0.0 0.255.255.255 area 0
	#network 11.0.0.0 0.255.255.255 area 3
	#area 3 virtual-link 15.255.255.254
	#redistribute rip subnets
	#exit
R5(config)#router rip
R5(config-router)#version 2
	#network 130.1.0.0
	#network 5.0.0.0
	#network 6.0.0.0
	#network 11.0.0.0
	#redistribute ospf 5 metric 1
	#^z